reviewText: This tape is very well done.  It covers seating, serving, handling silverware, and handshakes.  Stress is placed on good posture and poise.  Teens as well as adults would benefit from this tape.
this video is a great start for anyone wanting to spruce up their etiquette or start from the beginning.  it covers all the basics and is easy & fun to watch.  let's hope more people get into it!!
